description: Two young girls are standing next to each other in front of a wooden fence on a beach. The one with the black hair is wearing short white dress, and the blonde one is in rust, embroidered long frock with a long-patterned coat over it. Both are wearing black shoes. Both are looking at a grass strand the girl on the right is holding in her hands.

A young woman with freckles on her face is sitting on a beach deck in a dark blue embroidered tunic and a gold pendant with a heart on it. looking at the camera with a slight smile. She is holding a cup in her left hand and the right arm is on the deck.

A young woman with long blond hair wearing a white short dress with a plunging neckline sits on the floor looking at the camera with her right hand on her right knee. The left leg is resting on the floor. The look is embellished with blue and tea pink floral earrings.
A young woman with blonde hair in a beige bodycon dress is standing in front of a window in a hallway, looking at the camera with her arms crossed.

A young woman wearing a red dress and a black heavily embroidered shawl is standing in front of a wooden pillar at an open place, looking at her left with a slight smile. She is wearing a gold necklace with matching earrings and a ring in her left hand. The shawl has covered her right arm.

A young woman wearing an orange shalwar kameez with grey patterned dupatta carrying on her right shoulder stands in a lotus pond with the bow at the back of the kameez, looking at the camera from the back with her right hand slightly touching the dupatta. She is wearing minimal earrings and a ring in her right hand.

A monochrome image displays a woman on the left wearing a white dress with black patches on it, black sleeves, a wide black belt cinching the waist, a hijab and a wide-brimmed hat poses for a photo with her right hand on her waist looking straight into the camera with serious expressions. The woman on right is styling her by setting her sleeves with right hand on her shoulder.

Two young girls with sad faces are standing on a stone wall in the garden with the castle and greenery in the background. The one with black hair is wearing plain white pleated dress. The one on the left is wearing long black and white coat, black pants, and red gloves with checkered patterns, holding a cream handbag. Both are wearing black shoes.
